songs.title: So Cold (Interlude)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Turn up

[Verse]
When I reached in my drugs, I pulled out a big bankroll
As I scrolled down my contacts, cold as a zombone
(Hehe go right here)

[Interlude]
Cold freezer

[Outro]
Whatchu doing
Oh, kinda busy
Whatcha mean "Kinda busy"
I'm-I’m kinda busy, stop it (Shh)
Who's that you're talking to
Nobody, nobody, nobody
Who that? Future over there or something
